Hello Conscious Creators!

What new reality do you want to create for yourself in 2012?

It's HERE, time to test what you have learned about $$$$$$ and the Law of Attraction. Time to play - BINGO!!!!! Those who have a core belief that they can manifest money will bring more to them. 

I believe that if we gather our positive energies together, we will manifest $$$$$$$ together. It is sure to be a fun filled evening.

Join us in connecting with others who enjoy exploring endless possibilities, seeing all our experiences as a valuable life lesson and creating the change we desire.

 

This is the link to the Church http://stjosephparishmalden.com/index.html



We will be meeting from 5:45-6:15 PM in front of the Church. Doors open at 5:45PM.
Game Time 6:45

See you there!

Ellen
Organizer
